title: Who Is Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor, the Former Prince Arrested in the Epstein Inquiry?
summary_full: The brother of King Charles III was a popular member of the royal family and adored by his mother, Queen Elizabeth II. He fell from grace because of his friendship with Jeffrey Epstein.
